        <h1>Shot recipes you can actually recreate.</h1>
        <p class="sub">
          Descubri is building a shared library of <strong>Fuji film simulation recipes</strong>, <strong>Lightroom preset settings</strong>,
          <strong>LUT looks</strong>, and <strong>film stock recipes</strong>—paired with real photos and where they were shot.
        </p>

